Field Detail

board

public final CheckersBoard board
The current CheckersBoard such that this CheckersPlayerInterface is Player1.

gameOutcome

public final int gameOutcome
The CheckersGameManager's current game outcome at the time of this CheckersPlayerInterface.CheckersPlayerEvent creation. It will be one of CheckersGameManager.GAME_IN_PROGRESS, CheckersGameManager.INTERRUPTED, CheckersGameManager.DRAW, CheckersGameManager.PLAYER1_WINS, or CheckersGameManager.PLAYER2_WINS

maxMoves

public final int maxMoves
The maximum number of moves the Checkers game will last before it is declared a CheckersGameManager.DRAW.
